  "text": "The article is organized as follows. First, computing scheme for detection of boundary of area covered by a phenomena cloud with mobile sensors is described. Then we introduce several measures for assessing quality of a given sensing topology and statistical tools for analyzing the variability of these measures. Next, we introduce computing scheme for detecting the temporrily optimal sensing topology. Finally, the results of applications of our method to detect the heavy Proceedings of the Federated Conference on Computer Science and Information Systems pp. 865-872 DOI: 10.15439/2017F294 ISSN 2300-5963 ACSIS, Vol. 11 IEEE Catalog Number: CFP1785N-ART c 2017, PTIgas cloud are presented and discussed. Two more and less advanced gas dispersion models were taken into account: the box model [CITATION_1] and the advance model provided in SLAB [CITATION_2] .",
